**SCP-3279:** 잔상
**저자:** Popsioak
**원작:** http://www.scp-wiki.net/scp-3279
**역자:** [[*user Fluxman]]

> **파일명:** AB071_Merionis_hurrianae.jpg
> **저자:** AshLin
> **라이선스:** CC BY-SA 3.0
> **출처:** [https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:AB071_Merionis_hurrianae.JPG Wikimedia Commons]
[[include info:end]]
[[include :scpko:component:info-ayers
|lang=ko
